X_beta = sum_i beta_i X_\{s+1-i\}; w <- (X_\{s+1\}^T X_\{s+1\} + X_beta^T X_beta)^+ [X_\{s+1\}^T (T_s beta) + X_beta^T t_\{s+1\}],
then normalize w. After each component, deflate X by X <- X - t p^T with p = X^T t / (t^T t). A joint VAR(s) is fit
